ue that was deserialized from a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"corrupted serialized container then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" may be returned.  In this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"case, the proper thing to do is typically to use the appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"number of nul bytes in place of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":".  If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" is not fixed-sized"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is never returned."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the case that "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"text":" is already in serialized form, this function","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is ","type":"text"},{"code":"O(1)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":".  If the value is not already in serialized form,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"serialization occurs implicitly and is approximately ","type":"text"},{"code":"O(n)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in the size"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of the result."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To deserialize the data returned by this function, in addition to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"serialized data, you must know the type of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", and (if the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"machine might be different) the endianness of the machine that stored"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it. As a result, file formats or network messages that incorporate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"serialized "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"